Hi all,

Hope everybody enjoyed the holidays! In case you are already tired of
the games you got for xmas maybe give our new game Artefacts a try!
Imagine a world like Minecraft with the exception that instead of
cubic blocks you get to evolve your own blocks and use them to build
interesting things.

You can find the game here: http://cristi.itch.io/artefacts

To analyse how people play and what they evolve, the game sends some
anonymized data to us.

Looking forward to your comments. If you create interesting structures
please share pictures of them with us by email
(sebastian.risi@...).

Cheers,
Sebastian
